Javascript is a very interactive and powerful language. It is used to develop powerful games and apps. 

JavaScript is a cross-platform, object-oriented scripting language used to make webpages interactive 
(e.g., having complex animations, clickable buttons, popup menus, etc.). 
There are also more advanced server side versions of JavaScript such as Node.

Stage 1 commit

JavaScript is a programming language that adds interactivity to your website.
This happens in games, in the behavior of responses when buttons are pressed or with data entry on forms; 
with dynamic styling; with animation, etc.

